1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:55,540
=Episode 2=

3
00:00:59,240 --> 00:00:59,799
Move it!

4
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:04,480
When Her Highness wants you dead,

5
00:01:04,599 --> 00:01:05,959
no one can save you.

6
00:01:07,159 --> 00:01:08,439
Is this really the Princess's order?

7
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,599
What disregard for human life.

8
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:13,359
Her Highness has executed

9
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:15,560
countless slaves like you.

10
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,319
One more won't make a difference.

11
00:01:17,599 --> 00:01:19,120
Her Highness wouldn't even bat an eye.

12
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,439
Mother.

13
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,159
Ruyi, are you unwell?

14
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,040
Your Majesty.

15
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:40,599
Her Highness has been feeling dizzy
and fatigued lately,

16
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:41,719
with little appetite.

17
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:44,000
She must be tired from overwork.

18
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:56,959
We can't wait any longer.

19
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,879
Your symptoms get worse

20
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:00,680
the closer it gets to your birthday.

21
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:01,640
Mother.

22
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:03,680
I know my own body.

23
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,079
I have it under control.

24
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,920
Are you trying to kill yourself?

25
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,319
Summon all the male consorts
in the palace.

26
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,280
I want their heart-blood.

27
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:12,919
I won't

28
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:16,039
let any harm come to you.

29
00:02:33,140 --> 00:02:34,420
(Mo Shuo, Prince of Dongqing)

30
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:38,000
Sorry, I'm late.

31
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:45,319
Where's the roly-poly toy
Father gave me?

32
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:48,319
Where did I put it?

33
00:03:04,199 --> 00:03:06,000
I gave a clear order for your death.

34
00:03:07,039 --> 00:03:08,240
Why are you still alive?

35
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,159
Your Highness, you order my death

36
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:11,919
just because you don't trust me.

37
00:03:12,159 --> 00:03:13,479
You thought I'm a spy from the enemy.

38
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,560
I was born a slave.

39
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:16,759
My father died when I was young.

40
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,800
So I had to learn some martial skills.

41
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,520
I killed the two guards

42
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,400
in self-defense.

43
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:27,039
But I found this and waited to return it

44
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,639
for loyalty.

45
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:34,759
Aren't you afraid I'll kill you myself?

46
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,360
Your Highness is virtuous
and courageous.

47
00:03:38,319 --> 00:03:40,759
You can't be that cruel to
someone who's honest with you.

48
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,080
Return this to me,

49
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,319
and I'll spare you.

50
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:55,639
I take my duties as a husband seriously.

51
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:58,919
Since I've been intimate with
Your Highness,

52
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,000
you must take responsibility.

53
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,120
What responsibility?

54
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:05,560
In this world,

55
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,719
no man dared to ask me
to take responsibility.

56
00:04:08,879 --> 00:04:09,719
Right here,

57
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,680
on this bamboo raft,

58
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,759
Your Highness took my first kiss.

59
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,120
Since then,
I shall never change in this lifetime,

60
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:20,279
and I will follow you
to the ends of the earth.

61
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:23,879
So stubborn.

62
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:25,240
In your dreams.

63
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:28,360
You think you can show up
and leave from Ruyi Palace freely?

64
00:04:30,279 --> 00:04:31,399
Now that you've left,

65
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:33,920
you'll have to earn your way back.

66
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,839
Thank you for the guidance,
Your Highness.

67
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:43,040
I will make you take responsibility.

68
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:45,759
We'll see what you're made of

69
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,279
at the husband-selection ceremony.

70
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,720
Ke'er.

71
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,759
Get started.

72
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:52,759
Yes.

73
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:54,199
Am I late?

74
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,600
Your Highness, why is he here?

75
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,519
Should I order to execute him again?

76
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,600
He dares to risk his life
again and again.

77
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:11,759
Why not cast a long line
and wait for the big catch?

78
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,399
Let's find out what he's really after.

79
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,800
As everyone knows,

80
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:19,839
the rules of virtue, conduct,
and discipline for men

81
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:22,399
are the very foundation of Xiling.

82
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,319
If a man

83
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,240
does not know his place,

84
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:28,360
I suspect that even if
admitted into the Princess's mansion,

85
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,360
he'll never be content.

86
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,720
Gentlemen, a question for you.

87
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:38,199
About virtue, how do you interpret
"husband takes wife as his guide"?

88
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:41,639
A man should be pure in heart,
calm in mind, and true to himself.

89
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:43,720
Act with honor and live with order.

90
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,879
Be virtuous in deed, measured in words,

91
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:47,279
diligent in duties,
and dignified in appearance.

92
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:48,439
A man's body should never be defiled.

93
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:50,839
Always ready to serve his wife.

94
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:51,879
Tacky.

95
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:52,879
Cheesy.

96
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:54,360
A fossil.

97
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,879
Follow, obey, and submit to the wife.

98
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:58,800
Wait for wife patiently.

99
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,360
Remember her words, endure her moods,

100
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,279
and let go of your pride.

101
00:06:01,279 --> 00:06:03,120
Act cute. Play dumb.

102
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,600
Pretend to be a fossil.

103
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:05,680
It seems

104
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,120
I'll have to clear out the stables
at the mansion.

105
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:11,839
I wonder if these men will even fit in.

106
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,439
I'm not much of a scholar.

107
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,680
But living with my parents for decades,

108
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:18,199
I have learned something.

109
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,439
The tedious formalities in the classics

110
00:06:20,879 --> 00:06:22,560
cannot rival the true hearts
of a husband and wife.

111
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,600
Once your true heart is given,

112
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:26,240
you won't have any regrets.

113
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:29,079
Only then can you find happiness.

114
00:06:29,839 --> 00:06:31,319
Talk is cheap.

115
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:34,800
I've never seen a man
with such a true heart.

116
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,839
The bond between husband and wife

117
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:42,839
is just like this roly-poly toy.

118
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,439
Only when both sides are evenly matched

119
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:47,560
can they hold their ground

120
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,720
and never fall.

121
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:55,879
Xiling and Dongqing have been at war
for decades.

122
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:58,759
If you wish to serve Her Highness,

123
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,879
besides being virtuous and refined,

124
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,480
at critical moments,

125
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:04,920
you must protect her with your life.

126
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,319
Protect her with our lives?

127
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:13,319
Choose among white silk, poisoned wine,

128
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,800
and a dagger

129
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,439
to end yourselves.

130
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:19,560
That will prove your manhood.

131
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:20,600
Your Highness.

132
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,240
My family is bedridden with illness.

133
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,800
I'm afraid I'm also prone to sickness.

134
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:25,839
I fear your favor is
more than I deserve.

135
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,800
I am willing to die for Your Highness,

136
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,319
but on such a beautiful day,

137
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,720
if we are parted by death,

138
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:33,120
how can I take care of Your Highness
wholeheartedly?

139
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:34,800
Could we have another trial?

140
00:07:37,319 --> 00:07:39,319
Since you swore to return to the palace,

141
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:41,879
what answer do you give me?

142
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:45,600
Forgive me, but I cannot die here.

143
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,240
Your Highness.

144
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,600
There are too many losers here.

145
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:53,040
Throw them all out!

146
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,160
A pack of cowards.

147
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:55,600
Yes.

148
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,199
Your Highness.

149
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:06,680
Your Highness, I wonder

150
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,879
if you remember this wound on my chest?

151
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,240
It's the mark you left on me

152
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,920
when we first met.

153
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,439
You said you stabbed me

154
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,360
but also saved my life.

155
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,680
The roly-poly toy I found

156
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,120
has been returned to you.

157
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:36,159
Let this be my repayment

158
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:38,639
for your mercy in sparing my life
with that stab.
